$ ORA-28002: the password will expire within N days

*ORA-28002: the password will expire within N days* is more of a warning than an error. A
→ development/databases/Oracle/users-roles/users receives this warning when trying to log on and the password expiration date is going to be reached soon.

sa:
  The → development/databases/Oracle/SQL-Plus command `→ development/databases/Oracle/SQL-Plus/password`

  → development/databases/Oracle/errors[Other Oracle error messages] (such as
  → development/databases/Oracle/errors/ORA-28001_the-password-has-expired)
